text: Renate Holmes (born 30 August 1929) is a British alpine skier. She competed at the 1956 Winter Olympics and the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
